; 12-bit RGB444 Tile Data COE File
; Format: [RRRR][GGGG][BBBB] = 12 bits per pixel
; Tiles 0-9: Walls/floor, 10: Rock, 11: Barrel, 12-15: Arrows, 16-21: Stairs, 22-23: Lvl2 obs
;
; Memory Layout:
;   0x0000 - 0x17FF: Tile pixel data (24 tiles x 256 pixels)
;   0x1800 - 0x1B83: Tilemap 0 (Empty room)
;   0x1B84 - 0x1F07: Tilemap 1 (I-shape room)
;   0x1F08 - 0x228B: Tilemap 2 (Cross room)
;   0x228C - 0x260F: Tilemap 3 (Pillars room)
;   0x2610 - 0x2993: Tilemap 4 (Stair room)
;
; Tilemap addressing: addr = MAP_BASE + (map_id * 900) + row * 30 + col
;   Map 0 base: 0x1800 (Empty)
;   Map 1 base: 0x1B84 (I-shape)
;   Map 2 base: 0x1F08 (Cross)
;   Map 3 base: 0x228C (Pillars)
;   Map 4 base: 0x2610 (Stair)
;
; NOTE: Player projectile (shuriken) is in separate BRAM (blk_mem_gen_5)
;
